title: WinRAR 5.30 Final x86 & x64 +NEW Key
description:
This upload is the same as the previous one, but this one has A brand new key and activation method.



For those who have problems with the activation:




Step 1: Right-click on "Key" and Extract it with WinRAR to the desktop.


Step 2: Right-click on the "rarreg.key" file. Select "Copy" from the drop-down menu.


Step 3: Click on the desktop "Start" menu. Select "Computer" in Windows 7 and Vista and on "PC" in Windows 10.


Step 4: Double-click on the "C" drive and select the "Program Files" folder. Double-click to open the "WinRar" folder.


Step 5: Right-click in an empty place within the folder and select "Paste." The license key will copy to the WinRAR folder.


Step 6: Launch the WinRAR application and notice that "Evaluation copy" is no longer listed. The program is now fully activated
